{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-fable-5","id":"msg_011Cd7CQtoLdjnBVCzLPdBU4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01EangGAuhDASouZ8iTNXCum","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/tmp/arena-ws.UQkdWh/REPORT.md","content":"## Overview\n\nThis report covers 30 orders recorded in data/sales.csv between 2026-05-02 and 2026-05-21, spanning four regions (North, South, East, West) and four products. Total revenue was $7,154.44 across those 30 orders, averaging $238.48 per order with a median order value of $204.94.\n\n## Top Products\n\nGadget led all products with $2,392.00 in revenue from only 16 units, driven by its $149.50 unit price. Widget followed at $2,118.94 and appeared in 10 of the 30 orders, more than any other product. Doohickey earned $1,513.00 from 17 units. Sprocket earned the least, $1,130.50, despite moving 238 units — by far the highest volume — because of its $4.75 price.\n\n## Regional Performance\n\nNorth led with $2,176.35 in revenue, followed by East at $1,830.79 and South at $1,732.48. West trailed at $1,414.82, about 65% of North's total. Every region purchased all four products, but West placed only one Gadget order, while each other region placed two.\n\n## Recommendations\n\n- Focus sales effort on West, the weakest region ($1,414.82); it placed only one Gadget order versus two in every other region.\n- Review Sprocket pricing: 238 units sold, the highest volume, produced only $1,130.50, the lowest product revenue at $4.75 per unit.\n- Promote high-priced Gadget ($149.50) more widely; just 16 units generated $2,392.00, the top product revenue, so small volume gains matter.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2447,"cache_read_input_tokens":23515,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2447,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_g